ViTRec's output to what previous visualization\nrecommendation systems would generate, and to manually crafted visualizations\nused by practitioners. We conducted formative evaluations with ten genEpi\nexperts to assess the relevance and interpretability of our results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Oct 2020 18:21:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-26"}
