rientation\npreserving homeomorphism, we prove that the cohomology ring of $C_n^G(S)$ is\nKoszul, and that for some of these spaces the minimal model can be obtained out\nof a Cartan-Chevally-Eilenberg construction applied to graded Lie algebra\ncomputed in an earlier work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Oct 2020 12:18:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-26"}
